OL,3,CAI risks becoming 'weapon of mass
OL,4,Cdestruction of jobs', Mayor of London
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"Used responsibly, AI could enable us
OL,8,Fto transform our public services,
OL,9,Fturbocharge productivity and tackle
OL,10,Fsome of our most complex challenges `
OL,11,Ffrom cancer care to the climate crisis.
OL,13,F"But used recklessly, it could usher
OL,14,Fin a new era of mass unemployment,
OL,15,Faccelerated inequality and an
OL,16,Funprecedented concentration of wealth
OL,17,Fand power...
OL,19,F"We mustn't drift, absentmindedly,
OL,20,Finto a future we didn't ask for and
OL,21,Fdon't want.
