OL,3,CAI risks becoming 'weapon of mass
OL,4,Cdestruction of jobs', Mayor of London
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,F"We need to wake up and make a choice:
OL,8,Fseize the potential of AI and use it
OL,9,Fas a superpower for positive
OL,10,Ftransformation and creation, or
OL,11,Fsurrender to it and sit back and watch
OL,12,Fas it becomes a weapon of mass
OL,13,Fdestruction of jobs."
