OL,3,CAI risks becoming 'weapon of mass
OL,4,Cdestruction of jobs', Mayor of London
OL,5,Cwarns
OL,7,FWithout action, roles may vanish
OL,8,Ffaster than new ones are created, with
OL,9,Fentry-level jobs likely to be the
OL,10,Ffirst to go, "robbing our young people
OL,11,Fof that vital first step on the career
OL,12,Fladder," Sir Sadiq says.
OL,14,FHe will announce a taskforce
OL,15,Fcomprising experts from government,
OL,16,Fbusiness, the skills sector and the AI
OL,17,Findustry to conduct a review of the
OL,18,Ftechnology's impact on jobs to help
OL,19,Fassess how to develop Londoners'
OL,20,Fskills for the future so they remain
OL,21,Fcompetitive in the global jobs market.
